text.tspan: Now you have explored both houses. Did you notice the difference?
In fact, the "architecture" of each house can be represented like this:
In house A, no matter which door you open
- the bathroom leads to the living-room
- the living room leads to the kitchen
- the kitchen leads to the bathroom
In house B, no matter where you are
- the yellow door leads to the kitchen
- the pink door leads to the living-room
- the blue door leads to the bathroom
